1. Grasp shot glass 1 (shot1)
2. Fill shot1 with ingredient2
3. Grasp the shaker with the other hand
4. Pour ingredient from shot1 to the shaker
5. Leave the shaker on the table
6. Refill shot1 with ingredient1
7. Grasp the shaker again
8. Pour the ingredient from shot1 to the shaker
9. Shake the cocktail (now we have cocktail2 in the shaker)
10. Leave the shaker on the table and make shot1 clean and empty
11. Grasp the shaker again
12. Pour from the shaker to shot1 (now shot1 contains cocktail2)

13. Empty the shaker and make it clean
14. Repeat steps 1-13 for shots 2, 3 and 4 using the respective ingredients for cocktails 3, 1 and 4.
    For shot2 (cocktail3): ingredient1 & ingredient2
    For shot3 (cocktail1): ingredient3 & ingredient1
    For shot4 (cocktail4): ingredient2 & ingredient3

Upon completing these steps, each shot glass will contain the desired cocktail:

shot1 contains cocktail2, shot2 contains cocktail3, shot3 contains cocktail1, shot4 contains cocktail4.